{
  "stem": "719.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was [INAUDIBLE], where predominantly, the people are, like, half German, half Poles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was, like-- I don't know if you ever heard of Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Germans came in, they said they were Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then some Czechoslovakians did that, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When in the liberation came, they said, I never spoke German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was not a German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said that, but I know they did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, once the government changed, they were something else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's so.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What can you do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's the way the world is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this apartment, which was very comfortable, so the girls had their own room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we, I, found this close friend of theirs, which then later on was Henry's-- is Henry's wife.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Max, he's gone now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had, after the war, he had very heavy car accident, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He survived Auschwitz and was killed-- it was a head on collision in Bedford, Indiana.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He's gone now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I don't want to change the story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But his wife was also a friend of ours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all week, all the girls, we lived together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when-- and I began to look for family while living with those two cousins of mine, and the girls.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I began to find, search in my head, the address of my aunt, which was so wonderful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I kept on saying to myself, if she was in hiding, it only makes sense that the Belgian people did not give them, did not squeal, or, or tell on them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They must be alive somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And sure enough, it took months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Through the Red Cross, I sent a letter from Poland, in Polish, to this address that I memorized in my head.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
